```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('E', 'Ee')

print(insert_after_character('Hello, World!'))  # Helleo, Worlde!
print(insert_after_character('She sells seashells on the seashore'))  # She sells seashells on the seashorEe
print(insert_after_character('EEEEEE'))  # EeEeEeEeEeEe
print(insert_after_character(''))  # ''
```
